citations:
    citation-twoiaf-aegon-v:
        source: source-twoiaf
        properties:
            locator: "The Targaryen Kings: Aegon V"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Aegon V 'the Unlikely': married Betha Blackwood (Black Betha). Children: Duncan (Prince of Dragonflies), Jaehaerys II, Daeron, Shaera, Rhaelle. Jenny of Oldstones and the Ghost of High Heart prophecy. Tragedy at Summerhall in 259 AC. Ninepenny Kings / Band of Nine."
